title: Radio Row Day 3: Super Bowl Preview; Derrick Henry; Sandwiches; Jordan Mailata
itunes:title: Radio Row Day 3: Super Bowl Preview; Derrick Henry; Sandwiches; Jordan Mailata
description:
A jammed packed Super Bowl Preview! A convention center filled with heroes Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler preview Super Bowl 56 between the Los Angeles Rams and Cincinnati Bengals. Rapsheet stops by to start the show, Derrick Henry talks about his pre game shower habits and Jordan Mailata talks about Handsome Hank. The heroes give their locks and give their Super Bowl Sandwich props.
